- **Different channels = different sessions** — Telegram doesn't reuse webchat session
- **Each session loads its own model** — webchat can work while Telegram breaks
- **Gateway logs reveal truth** — always check logs before guessing
- **Ollama configuration affects ALL new sessions** — not just current one

